---
title: Asian-Style Beef Rice Bowl with Cucumber, Fried Egg & Soy Mayonnaise
description: Inject your night with a burst of flavour by combining oyster and soy sauce to marinate beef, then add it to aromatic garlic rice. Top this baby off with a fried egg, sunny side up (of course) and a dollop of soy mayo for a dish that’ll have you salivating long before you plate up.
